{
  "description": "A nighttime panoramic view of a city skyline with a brightly illuminated bridge in the foreground and colorful fireworks exploding in the sky above. The bridge, a modern suspension structure with numerous lights running along its length, stretches horizontally across a dark body of water. Behind the bridge, the city rises with a dense arrangement of illuminated buildings, creating a vibrant urban landscape. A notable skyscraper stands out among the others, with a bluish hue and the fireworks exploding directly above it. The fireworks display a variety of colors, including red, white, and blue. In the distance, a second, older style bridge is visible, adding depth to the composition. The overall scene conveys a sense of celebration and urban beauty.",
